<p>Word on the street is "The Guthernator" rode with Dave today.  Good going, Jennifer!  When are you going to join us?</p>
<p>So, Koster and I hit Sunshine today, determined to keep our heart rates below 175bpm.  No such luck.  Oh well.  Great ride just the same.  Koster reminded me that I'm a slow descender.  Where were you, Greg?</p>
<p>After a weekend of 7-8% relative humidity readings, today's 60% was muggy&mdash;though my family back east remind me that that's nothin'!  At least I only needed one water bottle.</p>